      <div type="edition" xml:lang="mi-Latn">
	<p>
	  <lb n="1"/>
	  <placeName key="pl:Kalyāṇa">kaliyaṇa<unclear>ṇa</unclear></placeName>
	  suvaṇakorasa <persName key="pers:Svāmidatta">sāmida<lb n="2" break="no"/>tasa</persName> saha saghana paniyaka deyadhamma
	</p>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  A cistern, the meritorious gift of the goldsmith
	  <persName key="pers:Svāmidatta">Svāmidatta</persName>
	  of <placeName key="pl:Kalyāṇa">Kalyāṇa</placeName> together
	  with the community of ascetics and lay-brothers.
	</p>
